com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Class FoldingLabelState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.FoldingLabelState

  • public final class FoldingLabelState
extends Object
    A data container representing the state of a label at a FolderNodeState or FoldingEdgeState.

    When the properties of the state are changed, these changes are reflected immediately in the Views.

    See Also:
    FoldingLabelOwnerState.getLabels(), FoldingLabelOwnerState.addLabel(String, ILabelModelParameter, ILabelStyle, SizeD, Object), FoldingLabelOwnerState.remove(FoldingLabelState)

      • asLabel

        public final ILabel asLabel()
        Returns an ILabel instance which represents this label state.

        The returned label is not present in any graph but may be passed to IFoldingView.getViewItem(com.yworks.yfiles.graph.IModelItem) to get the label state's view label in the folding view graph.

        Returns:
        An ILabel instance which represents this label state.
